Table 1: Comparison results (in %) adapting from GTAV to Cityscapes. All the prior methods but CDA use the whole training 
set of Cityscapes in training -thus their models see more target images than ours -and do not leave out a separate validation 
set for model selection. Unlike the others, FCAN directly works with the original image size. OutputAdapt (ResNet-101) 
pre-trains the model using both ImageNet [31] and MS COCO [22].
